<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <title>NeuraMD</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <link rel="icon" href="<%= image_path("logo/favicon.png") %>" type="image/png">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag :app, "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>

  <body class="nm-auth">
    <div class="nm-auth__backdrop" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="nm-auth__orb nm-auth__orb--a"></span>
      <span class="nm-auth__orb nm-auth__orb--b"></span>
      <span class="nm-auth__orb nm-auth__orb--c"></span>
      <span class="nm-auth__grid"></span>
    </div>

    <main class="nm-auth__shell">
      <section class="nm-auth__intro">
        <a href="/" class="nm-auth__brand">NeuraMD</a>
        <p class="nm-auth__eyebrow">Mapa vivo de notas</p>
        <h1 class="nm-auth__title">Entre direto no grafo e navegue o conhecimento como estrutura, nao como lista.</h1>
        <p class="nm-auth__copy">O layout de acesso agora segue a pagina principal: fundo amplo, atmosfera de rede e controles em caixas flutuantes.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="nm-auth__card-wrap">
        <% if notice.present? %>
          <div class="nm-auth__flash nm-auth__flash--notice"><%= notice %></div>
        <% end %>
        <% if alert.present? %>
          <div class="nm-auth__flash nm-auth__flash--alert"><%= alert %></div>
        <% end %>

        <div class="nm-auth__card">
          <%= yield %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
